vim file

opens in command mode
insert mode - i
extended command mode uses :

gg - begining of page
G end of page
w to move cursor forward word by word
b back word by word
nw
nb
u undo last word
U undo last line
yy copy line
nyy
p paste after
P paste before
:se nu - set number on lines
dw delete letter by letter backward (backspace)
x (del key)
dd delete entire line
ndd 
/ search word in file

:%s/search word/replace word/g